sentence: Item 5.02 Departure of Directors or Certain Officers; Election of Directors; Appointment of Certain Officers; Compensation Arrangements of Certain Officers (b) On January 5, 2010, Corcept Therapeutics Incorporated (the Company) was advised by Edward E. Penhoet, Ph.D., of his decision to resign from the Corcept Board of Directors due to time constraints associated with his appointment as a member of President Obama s Council of Advisors on Science and Technology (PCAST).
